Dialogue: 4,0:11:06.37,0:11:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vitaj späť.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:13.99,0:11:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:15.16,0:11:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zdá sa, že sa moje prianie stalo skutočnosťou.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:21.08,0:11:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma si spomenula na sľub s tvojou mamou.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S mojou mamou?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:29.84,0:11:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tu len jedna vec...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:34.43,0:11:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta neplače.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:37.04,0:11:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že odvtedy, čo som na tom takto zle.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pani?
Dialogue: 4,0:11:43.53,0:11:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Som šťastná, pretože budem znovuzrodená, ale je tu jedna vec, ktorá mi robí starosti.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On to všetko v sebe drží kvôli mne.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:52.34,0:11:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja som chcela, aby sa smial, hneval a plakal.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:02.15,0:12:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma sľubuje, že Jin-tan bude určite plakať!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem ti, Menma-chan.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:14.29,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže sa na teba spolieham.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:23.26,0:12:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale premýšľala som nad tým veľmi dlho, pretože som nemala potuchy, ako to urobiť.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:31.59,0:12:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže som požiadala všetkých, aby mi pomohli, a preto som všetkých zavolala.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:39.39,0:12:42.81,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Menma nemyslela na nič také ako šikanovanie.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:41.56,0:12:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aby splnila svoj sľub, tak prešla kvôli tomu takú dlhú cestu...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:42.81,0:12:50.79,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma nie je múdra, a tak chcela premýšľať s ostatnými, ako ťa rozplakať.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:50.79,0:12:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nakoniec sa to v ten deň...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... nepodarilo.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:58.50,0:13:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Možno je to pre teba ako trest.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:03.77,0:13:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie je trest a ani nič také!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som tam prísť, či by som o tom vedel alebo nie.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som ísť, bez ohľadu na čas a dôvody.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Na to miesto!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:16.27,0:13:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan, zase plačeš?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:21.09,0:13:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale vieš, ja by som bola šťastnejšia, keby som v tvojej tvári videla úsmev.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:28.26,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím, že je čas ti povedať zbohom.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:32.89,0:13:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkaj, ešte! Počkaj!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie som to len ja!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:40.91,0:13:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som ťa stretnúť!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:43.65,0:13:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vždy som sa s tebou chcel stretnúť!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som povedať tvoje meno!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:48.38,0:13:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som sa ti ospravedlniť.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som ti povedať, že ťa milujem.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan...
Dialogue: 4,0:13:53.25,0:13:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale toto isté ti chcú povedať aj ostatní!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci ťa milujú!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci sa chceli s tebou stretnúť!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci na teba čakajú!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Na našom mieste!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma...
Dialogue: 4,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan...
Dialogue: 4,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcel som ti splniť tvoje prianie.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milujem ťa, Jin-tan.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:28.98,0:14:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nie som sám...
Dialogue: 4,0:14:31.44,0:14:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to zábava.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem byť s tebou navždy!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:36.79,0:14:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola to zábava, preto chcem byť s tebou navždy...
Dialogue: 4,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jin-tan?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:48.86,0:14:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci...
Dialogue: 4,0:14:52.86,0:14:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J—
Dialogue: 4,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma? Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:55.78,0:14:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:56.21,0:14:57.66,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Jin-tan?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:58.15,0:14:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 4,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ona...?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je možné, že Menma...?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V žiadnom prípade...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje, kde si?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyjdi rýchlo.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:10.25,0:15:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:12.65,0:15:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Jin-tan!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.26,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:16.13,0:15:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 4,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To je hra na schovávačku.
Dialogue: 4,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo myslíš tým, hra na schovávačku?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-tan?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.24,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Menma!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Menma sa hrá na schovávačku?
Dialogue: 4,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schovávačka?
